{"_id":"3iTdt2NRgIyrychR","name":"Endormi","permission":{"default":0},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&gt;@Compendium[sfrpg.rules.Conditions]</p>\n<hr>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vous dormez et êtes @Compendium[world.conditions-fr.RxvbSB9ZgSCBu2jw]{Sans défense}. Tant que vous êtes endormi, vous subissez un malus de -10 aux tests de Perception effectués pour repérer quelque chose. Si vous réussissez un test de Perception pour repérer quelque chose malgré ce malus, vous vous réveillez automatiquement. Vous pouvez également vous réveiller si vous êtes giflé ou blessé. Un allié peut vous réveiller par une action simple.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"CRB.273","type":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"type":""},"area":{"value":null,"units":"","shape":"","effect":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","additional":"","per":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"parts":[],"effect":""},"damage":{"parts":[]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"","dc":null,"descriptor":""},"descriptors":[],"modifiers":[{"name":"Perception (Notice)","modifier":-10,"type":"untyped","effectType":"skill","valueAffected":"per","enabled":true,"source":"Condition (SRD)","notes":"While Asleep.","modifierType":"constant","condition":"","subtab":"misc","_id":"7777a761-d1bf-467b-859f-aaa872fd4569"}],"requirements":"Condition","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"abilityMods":{"parts":[]}},"sort":0,"flags":{"dynamiceffects":{"equipActive":false,"alwaysActive":false}},"img":"systems/sfrpg/icons/conditions/Asleep.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"4AkWDHGM6gHDepHN","name":"Agrippé","permission":{"default":0},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&gt;@Compendium[sfrpg.rules.Conditions]</p>\n<hr>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vous êtes entravé par une créature, un effet ou un piège.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vous ne&nbsp;pouvez pas vous déplacer et vous subissez un malus de -2 à votre&nbsp;classe d’armure, aux jets d’attaque, aux jets de sauvegarde de Réflexes,&nbsp;aux tests d’initiative et aux tests de&nbsp; caractéristique et de&nbsp;compétence basés sur la Dextérité, sauf ceux effectués pour agripper&nbsp;vous aussi votre adversaire ou pour échapper à la lutte (voir Lutte à&nbsp;la page 246). De plus, vous ne pouvez pas effectuer d’actions nécessitant&nbsp;vos deux mains (ou d’autres membres).</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vous ne pouvez pas faire&nbsp;d’attaques d’opportunité.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vous ne pouvez pas utiliser la Discrétion pour vous cacher de la&nbsp;créature qui vous agrippe, même si un pouvoir spécial vous permet de&nbsp;vous cacher quand cela est normalement impossible. Si vous devenez&nbsp;invisible, grâce à un sort ou un autre pouvoir, vous bénéficiez d’un&nbsp;bonus de circonstances de +2 à votre test effectué pour ne plus être&nbsp;agrippé mais aucun autre avantage ne vous est conféré.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"CRB.276","type":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"target":{"value":"","type":""},"area":{"value":null,"units":null,"shape":"","effect":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":null,"additional":"","per":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"ability":"int","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"parts":[],"effect":""},"damage":{"parts":[]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"","dc":null,"descriptor":"negate"},"descriptors":[],"modifiers":[{"name":"Grappled","modifier":-2,"type":"untyped","effectType":"ac","valueAffected":"both","enabled":true,"source":"Condition","notes":"","modifierType":"constant","condition":"","subtab":"misc","_id":"adf5f3cf-4f30-49a2-b828-3b2b3e93df07"},{"name":"Grappled","modifier":-2,"type":"untyped","effectType":"all-attacks","valueAffected":"","enabled":true,"source":"Condition","notes":"","modifierType":"constant","condition":"","subtab":"misc","_id":"dccb0409-cc76-4865-b142-d49625f86f42"},{"name":"Grappled","modifier":-2,"type":"untyped","effectType":"save","valueAffected":"reflex","enabled":true,"source":"Condition","notes":"","modifierType":"constant","condition":"","subtab":"misc","_id":"7dfe6bb7-6af9-4e25-a892-4cdf04d7b973"},{"name":"Grappled","modifier":-2,"type":"untyped","effectType":"initiative","valueAffected":"","enabled":true,"source":"Condition","notes":"","modifierType":"constant","condition":"","subtab":"misc","_id":"061cff37-b5e8-452b-a904-779dfa287325"},{"name":"Grappled","modifier":-2,"type":"untyped","effectType":"ability-skills","valueAffected":"dex","enabled":true,"source":"Condition","notes":"","modifierType":"constant","condition":"","subtab":"misc","_id":"5ab0115c-7536-4cf4-b394-b73b470d8191"}],"requirements":"Condition","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"abilityMods":{"parts":[]}},"sort":2300000,"flags":{"dynamiceffects":{"equipActive":false,"alwaysActive":false}},"img":"systems/sfrpg/icons/conditions/grappled.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"4MxAK5uS0zMNWhUK","name":"Agonisant","permission":{"default":0},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&gt;@Compendium[sfrpg.rules.Conditions]</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&gt;@Compendium[sfrpg.conditions.Dead] + @Compendium[sfrpg.conditions.Stable] + @Compendium[sfrpg.conditions.Unconscious]</p>\n<hr>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Une créature agonisante est @Compendium[world.conditions-fr.lf8pbezocjYIvR9y]{Inconscient} et sur le point de mourir.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Les créatures avec 0 point de vie qui ne sont pas stabilisées sont&nbsp;agonisantes. Une créature agonisante ne peut plus entreprendre aucune&nbsp;action et perd 1 point de persévérance chaque round à la fin de&nbsp;son tour, à moins qu’elle ne parvienne à se stabiliser. Une créature&nbsp;agonisante peut dépenser 3 PP pour se stabiliser et peut ensuite dépenser&nbsp;d’autres PP lors d’un round ultérieur pour gagner 1 point de&nbsp;vie et poursuivre le combat. Se stabiliser ou bénéficier de soins qui&nbsp;remontent les points de vie au-dessus de 0 met fin à l’état agonisant,&nbsp;tout comme la mort. Voir Blessures et mort à la page 250 pour plus&nbsp;d’informations.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"CRB.275","type":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"target":{"value":"","type":""},"area":{"value":null,"units":null,"shape":"","effect":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":null,"additional":"","per":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"ability":"int","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"parts":[],"effect":""},"damage":{"parts":[]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"","dc":null,"descriptor":"negate"},"descriptors":[],"modifiers":[],"requirements":"Condition","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"abilityMods":{"parts":[]}},"sort":1500000,"flags":{"dynamiceffects":{"equipActive":false,"alwaysActive":false}},"img":"systems/sfrpg/icons/conditions/dying.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"4WXJOFZ4s7TJUW6D","name":"Recroquevillé","permission":{"default":0},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&gt;@Compendium[sfrpg.rules.Conditions]</p>\n<hr>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vous êtes paralysé par la peur.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vous êtes @Compendium[world.conditions-fr.MZ8OoH1GE9qDMyCD]{Pris au dépourvu} et ne pouvez entreprendre aucune action.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"CRB.274","type":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"target":{"value":"","type":""},"area":{"value":null,"units":null,"shape":"","effect":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":null,"additional":"","per":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"ability":"int","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"parts":[],"effect":""},"damage":{"parts":[]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"","dc":null,"descriptor":"negate"},"descriptors":[],"modifiers":[],"requirements":"Condition","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"abilityMods":{"parts":[]}},"sort":1000000,"flags":{"dynamiceffects":{"equipActive":false,"alwaysActive":false}},"img":"systems/sfrpg/icons/conditions/cowering.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"7PPRS6krnvaTHbxh","name":"Fasciné","permission":{"default":0},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&gt;@Compendium[sfrpg.rules.Conditions]</p>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vous &ecirc;tes captiv&eacute;.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tant que vous avez l&rsquo;&eacute;tat fascin&eacute;, vous demeurez&nbsp;debout ou assis, ne pouvez faire aucune action autre que celle&nbsp;consistant &agrave; pr&ecirc;ter attention &agrave; l&rsquo;effet de votre fascination pendant&nbsp;toute sa dur&eacute;e. Vous subissez un malus de -4 aux tests de comp&eacute;tence&nbsp;effectu&eacute;s de mani&egrave;re passive en r&eacute;ponse &agrave; d&rsquo;autres actions, tels que&nbsp;les tests de Perception. Toute menace potentielle, telle qu&rsquo;une cr&eacute;ature&nbsp;hostile en approche, vous conf&egrave;re un nouveau jet de sauvegarde&nbsp;contre l&rsquo;effet de votre fascination. Toute menace &eacute;vidente, telle qu&rsquo;un&nbsp;individu qui d&eacute;gaine une arme, lance un sort ou vous vise avec une&nbsp;arme &agrave; distance, met automatiquement fin &agrave; l&rsquo;&eacute;tat.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Un alli&eacute; peut vous&nbsp;secouer pour vous lib&eacute;rer de l&rsquo;effet et mettre un terme &agrave; cet &eacute;tat par&nbsp;une action simple.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"CRB.276","type":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"target":{"value":"","type":""},"area":{"value":null,"units":null,"shape":"","effect":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":null,"additional":"","per":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"ability":"int","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"parts":[],"effect":""},"damage":{"parts":[]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"","dc":null,"descriptor":"negate"},"descriptors":[],"modifiers":[{"name":"Entranced","modifier":-4,"type":"untyped","effectType":"all-skills","valueAffected":"","enabled":true,"source":"Condition","notes":"","modifierType":"constant","condition":"","subtab":"misc","_id":"54c06ee6-5bdf-4015-acce-f294f1b201ad"}],"requirements":"Condition","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"abilityMods":{"parts":[]}},"sort":1900000,"flags":{"dynamiceffects":{"equipActive":false,"alwaysActive":false}},"img":"systems/sfrpg/icons/conditions/fascinated.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"8LdyXZl9PeXXFE8O","name":"Enflammé","permission":{"default":0},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&gt;@Compendium[sfrpg.rules.Conditions]</p>\n<hr>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vous avez pris feu.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tant que vous avez cet état, chaque round au&nbsp;début de votre tour, avant de faire vos actions (ou de tenter le jet de&nbsp;sauvegarde de Réflexes décrit ci-dessous), vous subissez le montant de dégâts de feu indiqué (ou 1d6 dégâts de feu si l’effet à l’origine de&nbsp;l’état enflammé n’indique aucun montant). Les dégâts de feu provenant&nbsp;de plusieurs sources infligeant l’état enflammé sont cumulatifs.&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">À la fin de chaque round pendant lequel vous êtes enflammé, vous&nbsp;pouvez effectuer un jet de Réflexes pour supprimer cet état. Le DD&nbsp;de ce jet de sauvegarde est égal à 10 + le montant de dégâts de feu&nbsp;infligés par l’état enflammé lors du round en cours. Si vous réussissez&nbsp;ce jet de sauvegarde, l’état enflammé disparaît. Vous pouvez effectuer&nbsp;un nouveau jet de sauvegarde chaque round pendant lequel vous avez&nbsp;cet état et vous bénéficiez d’un bonus de +2 pour chaque jet de sauvegarde&nbsp;que vous avez effectué lors des rounds consécutifs précédents.&nbsp;Vous pouvez également mettre automatiquement fin à cet état en&nbsp;plongeant dans une quantité d’eau suffisante. S’il n’y a pas assez d’eau&nbsp;à disposition, vous pouvez passer une action complexe à vous rouler&nbsp;par terre ou à étouffer le feu d’une manière ou d’une autre pour effectuer&nbsp;un nouveau jet de sauvegarde avec un bonus de +4 (plus les éventuels&nbsp;bonus conférés par les tentatives précédentes et consécutives&nbsp;ratées) et mettre un terme à l’état en cas de réussite.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"CRB.273","type":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"target":{"value":"","type":""},"area":{"value":null,"units":null,"shape":"","effect":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":null,"additional":"","per":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"ability":"int","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"parts":[],"effect":""},"damage":{"parts":[]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"","dc":null,"descriptor":"negate"},"descriptors":[],"modifiers":[],"requirements":"Condition","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"abilityMods":{"parts":[]}},"sort":800000,"flags":{"dynamiceffects":{"equipActive":false,"alwaysActive":false}},"img":"systems/sfrpg/icons/conditions/Burning.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"8rIj0ewW4bL8Uph5","name":"Confus","permission":{"default":0},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&gt;@Compendium[sfrpg.rules.Conditions]</p>\n<hr>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Votre esprit est embrouillé et vous ne pouvez plus agir normalement.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vous ne parvenez plus à distinguer vos alliés de vos ennemis&nbsp;et considérez, par conséquent, toutes les créatures comme des ennemis,&nbsp;même vos plus proches amis ou les membres de votre famille. Un&nbsp;allié qui souhaite vous lancer un sort bénéfique dont la portée est au&nbsp;contact doit réussir un jet d’attaque contre votre classe d’armure énergétique&nbsp;car vous n’êtes plus considéré comme une cible volontaire. Si&nbsp;vous êtes attaqué alors que vous êtes confus, vous attaquez toujours&nbsp;la dernière créature qui vous a agressé jusqu’à ce qu’elle soit morte&nbsp;ou hors de vue, sauf s’il vous est impossible de l’attaquer pendant&nbsp;le round en cours pour une raison ou une autre. Tant que vous êtes&nbsp;confus, vous ne pouvez pas faire d’attaques d’opportunité contre les&nbsp;créatures ou les choses qui ne sont pas déjà la cible de vos attaques.&nbsp;Si vous n’êtes pas déjà en train d’attaquer une cible, faites un jet sur&nbsp;la table suivante chaque round au début de votre tour pour savoir ce&nbsp;que vous faites lors du round en cours.</p>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>[[/r 1d100 #Confusion Table % Result]]</td>\n<td><strong>COMPORTEMENT</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>1–25</td>\n<td>Vous agissez normalement.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>26–50</td>\n<td>Vous ne faites rien, à part bredouiller des incohérences.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>51–75</td>\n<td>Vous vous infligez 1d8 + modificateur de For dégâts avec un objet quevous avez en main.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>76–100</td>\n<td>Vous attaquez la créature la plus proche.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Si vous ne pouvez pas accomplir l’action indiquée, vous ne faites&nbsp;rien, à part bredouiller des incohérences. Vos opposants ne bénéficient&nbsp;d’aucun avantage particulier lorsqu’ils vous attaquent.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"CRB.273","type":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"target":{"value":"","type":""},"area":{"value":null,"units":null,"shape":"","effect":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":null,"additional":"","per":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"ability":"str","actionType":"mwak","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"parts":[],"effect":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d8+@mod",""]]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"","dc":"","descriptor":"negate"},"descriptors":[],"modifiers":[],"requirements":"Condition","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"abilityMods":{"parts":[]}},"sort":900000,"flags":{"dynamiceffects":{"equipActive":false,"alwaysActive":false}},"img":"systems/sfrpg/icons/conditions/Confused.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"BVdjvpucmvQU4cc1","name":"Paniqué","permission":{"default":0},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&gt;@Compendium[sfrpg.rules.Conditions]</p>\n<hr>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vous lâchez tous ce que vous tenez et fuyez à votre vitesse maximale&nbsp;dans une direction aléatoire, en vous éloignant de la cause de&nbsp;votre frayeur et de toutes les autres menaces que vous rencontrez.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vous ne pouvez faire aucune autre action. De plus, vous subissez un&nbsp;malus de -2 à tous les tests de caractéristique, aux jets de sauvegarde&nbsp;et aux tests de compétence. Si vous êtes acculé, vous vous&nbsp;recroquevillez et n’attaquez pas, le plus souvent en utilisant l’action&nbsp;de défense totale en situation de combat et rien d’autre. Vous pouvez&nbsp;utiliser des pouvoirs spéciaux, y compris des sorts, pour fuir ; en fait,&nbsp;vous devez les utiliser si c’est là le seul moyen à votre disposition&nbsp;pour vous enfuir.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"CRB.276","type":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"target":{"value":"","type":""},"area":{"value":null,"units":null,"shape":"","effect":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":null,"additional":"","per":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"ability":"int","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"parts":[],"effect":""},"damage":{"parts":[]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"","dc":null,"descriptor":"negate"},"descriptors":[],"modifiers":[{"name":"Panicked","modifier":-2,"type":"untyped","effectType":"all-skills","valueAffected":"","enabled":true,"source":"Condition","notes":"","modifierType":"constant","condition":"","subtab":"misc","_id":"53e14bc1-051f-40cf-9a27-c7f8838a0780"},{"name":"Panicked","modifier":-2,"type":"untyped","effectType":"saves","valueAffected":"","enabled":true,"source":"Condition","notes":"","modifierType":"constant","condition":"","subtab":"misc","_id":"2e9a292c-d8db-474f-be57-0f150594c76d"}],"requirements":"Condition","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"abilityMods":{"parts":[]}},"sort":2900000,"flags":{"dynamiceffects":{"equipActive":false,"alwaysActive":false}},"img":"systems/sfrpg/icons/conditions/panicked.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"CvsDp0GvojxiF2jz","name":"Étourdi","permission":{"default":0},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&gt;@Compendium[sfrpg.rules.Conditions]</p>\n<hr>\n<p>Vous lâchez tout ce que vous tenez, vous ne pouvez pas faire d’actions&nbsp;et vous êtes @Compendium[world.conditions-fr.MZ8OoH1GE9qDMyCD]{Pris au dépourvu}.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"CRB.277","type":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"target":{"value":"","type":""},"area":{"value":null,"units":null,"shape":"","effect":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":null,"additional":"","per":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"ability":"int","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"parts":[],"effect":""},"damage":{"parts":[]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"","dc":null,"descriptor":"negate"},"descriptors":[],"modifiers":[],"requirements":"Condition","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"abilityMods":{"parts":[]}},"sort":3700000,"flags":{"dynamiceffects":{"equipActive":false,"alwaysActive":false}},"img":"systems/sfrpg/icons/conditions/stunned.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"D8JvCEmOiWKe2UDx","name":"Assourdi","permission":{"default":0},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&gt;@Compendium[sfrpg.rules.Conditions]</p>\n<hr>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vous n’entendez plus rien.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vous subissez un malus de -4 aux tests&nbsp;d’initiative et aux tests de Perception opposés, et vous ratez automatiquement&nbsp;les tests de Perception basés sur l’ouïe. Les personnages longtemps assourdis commencent à s’habituer à ces inconvénients et&nbsp;peuvent en surmonter certains.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"CRB.275","type":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"target":{"value":"","type":""},"area":{"value":null,"units":null,"shape":"","effect":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":null,"additional":"","per":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"ability":"int","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"parts":[],"effect":""},"damage":{"parts":[]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"","dc":null,"descriptor":"negate"},"descriptors":[],"modifiers":[{"name":"Perception (Opposed)","modifier":-4,"type":"untyped","effectType":"skill","valueAffected":"per","enabled":true,"source":"Condition","notes":"","modifierType":"constant","condition":"","subtab":"misc","_id":"b325f976-e17f-4ade-a640-2e736fd2d350"},{"name":"Initiative","modifier":-4,"type":"untyped","effectType":"initiative","valueAffected":"","enabled":true,"source":"Condition","notes":"","modifierType":"constant","condition":"","subtab":"misc","_id":"b08bd1bb-bb45-44d0-811c-ab6dddfe843c"}],"requirements":"Condition","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"abilityMods":{"parts":[]}},"sort":1400000,"flags":{"dynamiceffects":{"equipActive":false,"alwaysActive":false}},"img":"systems/sfrpg/icons/conditions/deafened.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"DtwiUWi8dpzkq4tM","name":"Effrayé","permission":{"default":0},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&gt;@Compendium[sfrpg.rules.Conditions]</p>\n<hr>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vous fuyez du mieux possible la cause de votre frayeur.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Si vous ne&nbsp;pouvez pas fuir, vous pouvez combattre à la place. Vous subissez un malus&nbsp;de -2 aux tests de caractéristique, aux jets d’attaque, aux jets de sauvegarde&nbsp;et aux tests de compétence. Vous pouvez utiliser des pouvoirs&nbsp;spéciaux, notamment des sorts, pour fuir ; en fait, vous devez les utiliser&nbsp;si c’est là le seul moyen à votre disposition pour vous enfuir. Si vous&nbsp;êtes déjà effrayé puis assujetti à un autre effet qui devrait lui aussi vous&nbsp;effrayer, la durée du deuxième effet s’ajoute à celle de l’état effrayé.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"CRB.276","type":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"target":{"value":"","type":""},"area":{"value":null,"units":null,"shape":"","effect":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":null,"additional":"","per":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"ability":"int","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"parts":[],"effect":""},"damage":{"parts":[]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"","dc":null,"descriptor":"negate"},"descriptors":[],"modifiers":[{"name":"Frightened","modifier":-2,"type":"untyped","effectType":"all-skills","valueAffected":"both","enabled":true,"source":"Condition","notes":"","modifierType":"constant","condition":"","subtab":"misc","_id":"34ea6bbe-b405-4412-a31a-5a3e279ace48"},{"name":"Frightened","modifier":-2,"type":"untyped","effectType":"all-attacks","valueAffected":"","enabled":true,"source":"Condition","notes":"","modifierType":"constant","condition":"","subtab":"misc","_id":"9b06ec3d-d28c-401c-8651-b1a8c356d3e2"},{"name":"Frightened","modifier":-2,"type":"untyped","effectType":"saves","valueAffected":"","enabled":true,"source":"Condition","notes":"","modifierType":"constant","condition":"","subtab":"misc","_id":"aecb8c8e-4582-44d8-800b-b0b8115449b9"}],"requirements":"Condition","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"abilityMods":{"parts":[]}},"sort":2200000,"flags":{"dynamiceffects":{"equipActive":false,"alwaysActive":false}},"img":"systems/sfrpg/icons/conditions/frightened.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"H51jmhxF9XuwDOE7","name":"Stabilisé","permission":{"default":0},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&gt;@Compendium[sfrpg.rules.Conditions]</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&gt;@Compendium[sfrpg.conditions.Dying] + @Compendium[sfrpg.conditions.Dead] + @Compendium[sfrpg.conditions.Unconscious]</p>\n<hr>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Si vous étiez agonisant mais que vous avez dépensé des points de&nbsp;persévérance pour vous stabiliser (voir Utiliser des points de persévérance&nbsp;à la page 250 dans Blessures et mort) ou si un allié vous soigne,&nbsp;vous êtes stabilisé. Vous n’êtes alors plus agonisant mais toujours&nbsp;inconscient.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"CRB.277","type":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"target":{"value":"","type":""},"area":{"value":null,"units":null,"shape":"","effect":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":null,"additional":"","per":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"ability":"int","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"parts":[],"effect":""},"damage":{"parts":[]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"","dc":null,"descriptor":"negate"},"descriptors":[],"modifiers":[],"requirements":"Condition","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"abilityMods":{"parts":[]}},"sort":3500000,"flags":{"dynamiceffects":{"equipActive":false,"alwaysActive":false}},"img":"systems/sfrpg/icons/conditions/stable.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"JGFn4MrDZ6X5vrzU","name":"Fatigué","permission":{"default":0},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&gt;@Compendium[sfrpg.rules.Conditions]</p>\n<hr>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vous ne pouvez plus courir ou charger, et vous subissez un malus&nbsp;de -1 à la CA, aux jets d’attaque, aux jets de dégâts au corps à corps,&nbsp;aux jets de sauvegarde de Réflexes, aux tests d’initiative et aux tests&nbsp;de caractéristique et de compétence basés sur la Force et la Dextérité.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Le volume que vous pouvez transporter sans être encombré&nbsp;est réduit de 1. Si vous êtes fatigué et que vous vous consacrez à&nbsp;une activité qui devrait normalement provoquer de la fatigue, vous&nbsp;devenez épuisé à la place. Vous n’êtes plus fatigué après 8 heures de&nbsp;repos complet.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"CRB.276","type":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"target":{"value":"","type":""},"area":{"value":null,"units":null,"shape":"","effect":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":null,"additional":"","per":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"ability":"int","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"parts":[],"effect":""},"damage":{"parts":[]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"","dc":null,"descriptor":"negate"},"descriptors":[],"modifiers":[{"name":"Fatigued","modifier":-1,"type":"untyped","effectType":"ac","valueAffected":"both","enabled":true,"source":"Condition","notes":"","modifierType":"constant","condition":"","subtab":"misc","_id":"9a31d03e-3a10-40b1-99ec-7958b4b166f0"},{"name":"Fatigued","modifier":-1,"type":"untyped","effectType":"all-attacks","valueAffected":"","enabled":true,"source":"Condition","notes":"","modifierType":"constant","condition":"","subtab":"misc","_id":"56c19806-7626-4804-9229-8572c8065f78"},{"name":"Fatigued","modifier":-1,"type":"untyped","effectType":"melee-damage","valueAffected":"","enabled":true,"source":"Condition","notes":"","modifierType":"constant","condition":"","subtab":"misc","_id":"41867c1e-b0a5-4ecf-bb7d-c163c4b72db4"},{"name":"Fatigued","modifier":-1,"type":"untyped","effectType":"save","valueAffected":"reflex","enabled":true,"source":"Condition","notes":"","modifierType":"constant","condition":"","subtab":"misc","_id":"8587ec88-3bdd-473c-8ef0-b154ddb9a681"},{"name":"Fatigued","modifier":-1,"type":"untyped","effectType":"initiative","valueAffected":"","enabled":true,"source":"Condition","notes":"","modifierType":"constant","condition":"","subtab":"misc","_id":"bc9009e4-a377-4037-b4f4-e1acca4770d6"},{"name":"Fatigued","modifier":-1,"type":"untyped","effectType":"ability-skills","valueAffected":"str","enabled":true,"source":"Condition","notes":"","modifierType":"constant","condition":"","subtab":"misc","_id":"4e2ace7a-9d40-4955-abd7-dc5195aa1d31"},{"name":"Fatigued","modifier":-1,"type":"untyped","effectType":"ability-skills","valueAffected":"dex","enabled":true,"source":"Condition","notes":"","modifierType":"constant","condition":"","subtab":"misc","_id":"fb55db32-8cd6-4240-ac6e-3d14a105c2e6"}],"requirements":"Condition","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"abilityMods":{"parts":[]}},"sort":2000000,"flags":{"dynamiceffects":{"equipActive":false,"alwaysActive":false}},"img":"systems/sfrpg/icons/conditions/fatigued.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"K1Df65N6e1xHaDGW","name":"Cassé (Vehicule)","permission":{"default":0},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&gt;@Compendium[sfrpg.rules.Broken]</p>\n<hr>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Les objets ayant subi un montant de dégâts supérieur à la moitié de&nbsp;leur total de points de résistance obtiennent l’état cassé, ce qui signifie&nbsp;qu’ils sont moins efficaces pour accomplir les tâches auxquelles ils&nbsp;sont destinés. L’état cassé engendre les effets suivants, en fonction&nbsp;de l’objet en question. Vous trouverez les informations sur la solidité&nbsp;et les points de résistance des armes et des armures à la page 409.</p>\n<hr>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Si l’objet est un <strong>véhicule</strong>, il subit un malus de -2 à sa CA et au DD&nbsp;des collisions, son modificateur de Pilotage est réduit de 2, et sa vitesse&nbsp;de déplacement normale ainsi que son km/h sont diminués de&nbsp;moitié. (Voir la page 228 au chapitre 7 pour plus d’informations sur les&nbsp;véhicules cassés et détruits.)</p>\n<hr>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Les objets affublés de l’état cassé, quel que soit leur type, peuvent&nbsp;être revendus pour la moitié de leur prix de revente normal (généralement&nbsp;5 % du prix d’achat de l’objet). Un objet peut être réparé avec le&nbsp;sort de réparation ou de réparation intégrale lancé par un personnage&nbsp;dont le niveau de lanceur de sorts est égal ou supérieur au niveau de&nbsp;l’objet.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Les objets perdent l’état cassé si le sort permet à l’objet de&nbsp;récupérer la moitié ou plus de son nombre de points de vie d’origine.</p>\n<hr>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Il est également possible de réparer les objets magiques avec la&nbsp;compétence de Mysticisme (voir page 144 pour plus d’informations)&nbsp;et les objets technologiques avec la compétence d’Ingénierie (voir&nbsp;page 142 pour plus d’informations). On peut réparer les objets hybrides&nbsp;avec l’une ou l’autre de ces compétences.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">La plupart des réparateurs d’objets magiques ou technologiques font payer 10 % du prix d’achat d’origine de l’objet pour réparer ces dégâts (ou plus si l’objet est détruit ou sévèrement endommagé).</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"CRB.273","type":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"target":{"value":"","type":""},"area":{"value":null,"units":null,"shape":"","effect":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":null,"additional":"","per":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"ability":"int","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"parts":[],"effect":""},"damage":{"parts":[]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"","dc":null,"descriptor":"negate"},"descriptors":[],"modifiers":[],"requirements":"Condition","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"abilityMods":{"parts":[]}},"sort":600000,"flags":{"dynamiceffects":{"equipActive":false,"alwaysActive":false}},"img":"systems/sfrpg/icons/conditions/Broken.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"LoRydw1D4bqlbkA2","name":"Nauséeux","permission":{"default":0},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&gt;@Compendium[sfrpg.rules.Conditions]</p>\n<hr>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vous souffrez de maux d’estomac.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vous ne pouvez plus attaquer,&nbsp;lancer des sorts, vous concentrer sur des sorts ou faire quoi que ce soit d’autres qui nécessitent votre attention. Vous ne pouvez faire qu’une&nbsp;seule action de mouvement et rien d’autre chaque tour.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"CRB.276","type":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"target":{"value":"","type":""},"area":{"value":null,"units":null,"shape":"","effect":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":null,"additional":"","per":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"ability":"int","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"parts":[],"effect":""},"damage":{"parts":[]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"","dc":null,"descriptor":"negate"},"descriptors":[],"modifiers":[],"requirements":"Condition","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"abilityMods":{"parts":[]}},"sort":2500000,"flags":{"dynamiceffects":{"equipActive":false,"alwaysActive":false}},"img":"systems/sfrpg/icons/conditions/nauseated.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"MZ8OoH1GE9qDMyCD","name":"Pris au dépourvu","permission":{"default":0},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&gt;@Compendium[sfrpg.rules.Conditions]</p>\n<hr>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Au début d’un combat, si vous êtes surpris, vous êtes également&nbsp;pris au dépourvu jusqu’au moment où vous devenez conscient du combat&nbsp;et que vous avez eu l’occasion d’agir. Vous pouvez également être&nbsp;pris au dépourvu par de nombreux autres effets. Vous subissez un&nbsp;malus de -2 à votre CA et ne pouvez pas effectuer de réactions lorsque&nbsp;vous êtes pris au dépourvu.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"CRB.276","type":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"target":{"value":"","type":""},"area":{"value":null,"units":null,"shape":"","effect":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":null,"additional":"","per":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"ability":"int","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"parts":[],"effect":""},"damage":{"parts":[]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"","dc":null,"descriptor":"negate"},"descriptors":[],"modifiers":[{"name":"Flat-Footed","modifier":-2,"type":"untyped","effectType":"ac","valueAffected":"both","enabled":true,"source":"Condition","notes":"","modifierType":"constant","condition":"","subtab":"misc","_id":"34ea6bbe-b405-4412-a31a-5a3e279ace48"}],"requirements":"Condition","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"abilityMods":{"parts":[]}},"sort":2100000,"flags":{"dynamiceffects":{"equipActive":false,"alwaysActive":false}},"img":"systems/sfrpg/icons/conditions/flatfooted.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"NV4qXRDgb7zTNkW2","name":"Paralysé","permission":{"default":0},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&gt;@Compendium[sfrpg.rules.Conditions]</p>\n<hr>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vous êtes presque complètement immobilisé sur place et incapable&nbsp;de mouvoir votre corps. Vous pouvez à peine vous tortiller, bouger vos&nbsp;yeux, etc. Vous n’êtes pas sans défense pour autant, même si on considère&nbsp;que vous avez un modificateur de Dextérité de -5. Vous pouvez&nbsp;effectuer des actions purement mentales mais pas physiques. Vous&nbsp;chutez si vous êtes en train de voler lorsque vous devenez paralysé&nbsp;et que votre capacité à voler dépend de moyens physiques (avec&nbsp;des ailes, par exemple). Vous pouvez vous noyer si vous êtes en train&nbsp;de nager quand vous devenez paralysé (voir Asphyxie et noyade à la&nbsp;page 404). Une créature peut traverser l’emplacement que vous occupez,&nbsp;qu’elle soit votre alliée ou non. Cependant, chaque case que vous&nbsp;occupez compte comme 2 cases de déplacement.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"CRB.276","type":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"target":{"value":"","type":""},"area":{"value":null,"units":null,"shape":"","effect":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":null,"additional":"","per":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"ability":"int","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"parts":[],"effect":""},"damage":{"parts":[]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"","dc":null,"descriptor":"negate"},"descriptors":[],"modifiers":[],"requirements":"Condition","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"abilityMods":{"parts":[]}},"sort":3000000,"flags":{"dynamiceffects":{"equipActive":false,"alwaysActive":false}},"img":"systems/sfrpg/icons/conditions/paralyzed.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"OwZA6flUQPH0jPA0","name":"Encombré","permission":{"default":0},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&gt;@Compendium[sfrpg.rules.Conditions]</p>\n<hr>\n<p>Toutes vos vitesses de déplacement sont réduites de 3 mètres,&nbsp;votre bonus de Dextérité maximum à la CA est réduit à +2 et vous&nbsp;subissez un malus de -5 aux tests basés sur la Force et la Dextérité (ou&nbsp;le malus d’armure aux tests de votre armure s’il est plus élevé).</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"CRB.275","type":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"target":{"value":"","type":""},"area":{"value":null,"units":null,"shape":"","effect":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":null,"additional":"","per":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"ability":"int","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"parts":[],"effect":""},"damage":{"parts":[]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"","dc":null,"descriptor":"negate"},"descriptors":[],"modifiers":[{"name":"Speeds (All)","modifier":0,"type":"untyped","effectType":"skill","valueAffected":"acr","enabled":false,"source":"Condition","notes":"INCOMPLETE.","modifierType":"constant","condition":"","subtab":"misc","_id":"95d86834-40ad-4367-86a2-a281bae55066"},{"name":"Max Dex Bonus Cap","modifier":0,"type":"untyped","effectType":"skill","valueAffected":"acr","enabled":true,"source":"Condition","notes":"INCOMPLETE.","modifierType":"constant","condition":"","subtab":"misc","_id":"b35c7a74-98c0-47cd-9ba3-0cfc48ccbb2e"}],"requirements":"Condition","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"abilityMods":{"parts":[]}},"sort":1600000,"flags":{"dynamiceffects":{"equipActive":false,"alwaysActive":false}},"img":"systems/sfrpg/icons/conditions/encumbered.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"QnGpBSHSTiszjPSb","name":"En apesanteur","permission":{"default":0},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&gt;@Compendium[sfrpg.rules.Conditions]</p>\n<hr>\n<p>Vous êtes désorienté et flottez dans un environnement où la gravité&nbsp;est nulle.</p>\n<p>Vous ne pouvez pas faire d’actions de mouvement pour vous&nbsp;déplacer, ramper ou faire un déplacement prudent. Vous êtes @Compendium[world.conditions-fr.MZ8OoH1GE9qDMyCD]{Pris au dépourvu}&nbsp;et subissez un malus de -2 aux jets&nbsp; d’attaque.</p>\n<p>Vous devez utiliser un moyen de propulsion pour vous redresser&nbsp;ou pour vous agripper à un objet stable tel qu’un mur ou une&nbsp;échelle (généralement par une action de mouvement) afin de mettre&nbsp;un terme à cet état. Voir Gravité zéro à la page 402 pour plus&nbsp;d’informations.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"CRB.276","type":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"target":{"value":"","type":""},"area":{"value":null,"units":null,"shape":"","effect":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":null,"additional":"","per":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"ability":"int","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"parts":[],"effect":""},"damage":{"parts":[]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"","dc":null,"descriptor":"negate"},"descriptors":[],"modifiers":[{"name":"Off-Kilter","modifier":-2,"type":"untyped","effectType":"all-attacks","valueAffected":"","enabled":true,"source":"Condition","notes":"","modifierType":"constant","condition":"","subtab":"misc","_id":"d0a80e25-d152-47a5-b497-91dc39eb9e99"}],"requirements":"Condition","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"abilityMods":{"parts":[]}},"sort":2600000,"flags":{"dynamiceffects":{"equipActive":false,"alwaysActive":false}},"img":"systems/sfrpg/icons/conditions/offkilter.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"RxvbSB9ZgSCBu2jw","name":"Sans défense","permission":{"default":0},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&gt;@Compendium[sfrpg.rules.Conditions]</p>\n<hr>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vous êtes attaché, @Compendium[world.conditions-fr.3iTdt2NRgIyrychR]{Endormi}, @Compendium[world.conditions-fr.lf8pbezocjYIvR9y]{Inconscient} ou, par ailleurs, complètement à la merci d’un adversaire. On considère alors que vous avez une Dextérité de 0 (ce qui vous donne un modificateur de Dextérité de -5) et les attaques au corps à corps contre vous bénéficient d’un bonus supplémentaire de +4 (qui équivaut au bonus lorsqu’on attaque une cible à terre). Les attaques à distance contre vous ne bénéficient d’aucun bonus spécial.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"CRB.276","type":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"target":{"value":"","type":""},"area":{"value":null,"units":null,"shape":"","effect":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":null,"additional":"","per":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"ability":"int","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"parts":[],"effect":""},"damage":{"parts":[]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"","dc":null,"descriptor":"negate"},"descriptors":[],"modifiers":[{"name":"AC against Melee Attacks","modifier":-4,"type":"untyped","effectType":"ac","valueAffected":"both","enabled":true,"source":"Condition","notes":"AC against Melee Attacks.","modifierType":"constant","condition":"","subtab":"misc","_id":"6c4dad83-99a0-4d7c-a7ad-f7167f1fb898"}],"requirements":"Condition","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"abilityMods":{"parts":[]}},"sort":2400000,"flags":{"dynamiceffects":{"equipActive":false,"alwaysActive":false}},"img":"systems/sfrpg/icons/conditions/helpless.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"XeRGqHVtcZ7vsgJ0","name":"À terre","permission":{"default":0},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&gt;@Compendium[sfrpg.rules.Conditions]</p>\n<hr>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vous êtes affalé par terre. Vous subissez un malus de -4 aux jets d’attaque&nbsp;au corps à corps. Vous bénéficiez d’un bonus de +4 à votre classe&nbsp;d’armure contre les attaques à distance mais vous subissez un malus&nbsp;de -4 à votre classe d’armure contre les attaques au corps à corps. Vous&nbsp;relever lorsque vous êtes à terre est une action de mouvement.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"CRB.277","type":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"target":{"value":"","type":""},"area":{"value":null,"units":null,"shape":"","effect":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":null,"additional":"","per":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"ability":"int","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"parts":[],"effect":""},"damage":{"parts":[]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"","dc":null,"descriptor":"negate"},"descriptors":[],"modifiers":[{"name":"Prone","modifier":-4,"type":"untyped","effectType":"melee-attacks","valueAffected":"","enabled":true,"source":"Condition","notes":"","modifierType":"constant","condition":"","subtab":"misc","_id":"0cce6d75-e03b-4ba6-bc66-48b00c0e9ac7"},{"name":"AC against Ranged Attacks","modifier":4,"type":"untyped","effectType":"ac","valueAffected":"both","enabled":true,"source":"Condition","notes":"Against Ranged attacks.","modifierType":"constant","condition":"","subtab":"misc","_id":"ca5db92b-5e41-4ad6-b36d-9afb48825189"},{"name":"AC against Melee Attacks","modifier":-4,"type":"untyped","effectType":"ac","valueAffected":"both","enabled":true,"source":"Condition","notes":"AC against Melee Attacks.","modifierType":"constant","condition":"","subtab":"misc","_id":"b4741240-87bd-4f61-bc23-db280a640cf0"}],"requirements":"Condition","recharge":{"v