{"_id":"XgK4EdO5D3Fj3iWz","name":"Immobilisé","permission":{"default":0},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&gt;@Compendium[sfrpg.rules.Conditions]</p>\n<hr>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vous êtes fermement ligoté sur place et êtes ainsi limité à quelques actions seulement. Tant que vous êtes immobilisé, vous ne pouvez plus vous déplacer et vous êtes @Compendium[world.conditions-fr.MZ8OoH1GE9qDMyCD]{Pris au dépourvu}. Vous subissez également un malus supplémentaire de -4 à votre classe d’armure, aux jets d’attaque, aux jets de sauvegarde de Réflexes, aux tests d’initiative et aux tests de caractéristique et de compétence basés sur la Dextérité (ces malus remplacent ceux de l’état agrippé et s’appliquent également aux tentatives pour agripper votre adversaire ou pour vous libérer ; voir Lutte à la page 246).</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L’éventail des actions que vous pouvez effectuer&nbsp;est limité. Vous ne pouvez effectuer aucune action nécessitant&nbsp;l’utilisation de vos membres mais vous pouvez toujours tenter de vous&nbsp;libérer, généralement grâce à un jet d’attaque ou un test d’Acrobaties.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vous ne pouvez pas faire d’attaques d’opportunité lorsque vous êtes&nbsp;immobilisé mais vous pouvez toujours effectuer des actions verbales&nbsp;ou mentales, comme l’incantation de sorts par exemple.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"CRB.277","type":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"target":{"value":"","type":""},"area":{"value":null,"units":null,"shape":"","effect":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":null,"additional":"","per":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"ability":"int","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"parts":[],"effect":""},"damage":{"parts":[]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"","dc":null,"descriptor":"negate"},"descriptors":[],"modifiers":[{"name":"Pinned","modifier":-4,"type":"untyped","effectType":"ac","valueAffected":"both","enabled":true,"source":"Condition","notes":"","modifierType":"constant","condition":"","subtab":"misc","_id":"81c4f254-8e3d-4b76-9555-ccb42f3ef47a"},{"name":"Pinned","modifier":-4,"type":"untyped","effectType":"all-attacks","valueAffected":"","enabled":true,"source":"Condition","notes":"","modifierType":"constant","condition":"","subtab":"misc","_id":"7fc65f0c-2d70-4127-995c-b20085ce8336"},{"name":"Pinned","modifier":-4,"type":"untyped","effectType":"save","valueAffected":"reflex","enabled":true,"source":"Condition","notes":"","modifierType":"constant","condition":"","subtab":"misc","_id":"fcfb040a-b6a4-42c0-b809-b5aa0d3d4723"},{"name":"Pinned","modifier":-4,"type":"untyped","effectType":"initiative","valueAffected":"","enabled":true,"source":"Condition","notes":"","modifierType":"constant","condition":"","subtab":"misc","_id":"3d6c2c04-3c2c-4b9f-a8d7-b1da528b800a"},{"name":"Pinned","modifier":-4,"type":"untyped","effectType":"ability-skills","valueAffected":"dex","enabled":true,"source":"Condition","notes":"","modifierType":"constant","condition":"","subtab":"misc","_id":"5d64556e-38f6-4387-92ec-f1d3d837547e"}],"requirements":"Condition","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"abilityMods":{"parts":[]}},"sort":3100000,"flags":{"dynamiceffects":{"equipActive":false,"alwaysActive":false}},"img":"systems/sfrpg/icons/conditions/pinned.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"YEfXWOqDH3s8dvvK","name":"Cassé (Armure)","permission":{"default":0},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&gt;@Compendium[sfrpg.rules.Broken]</p>\n<hr>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Les objets ayant subi un montant de dégâts supérieur à la moitié de&nbsp;leur total de points de résistance obtiennent l’état cassé, ce qui signifie&nbsp;qu’ils sont moins efficaces pour accomplir les tâches auxquelles ils&nbsp;sont destinés. L’état cassé engendre les effets suivants, en fonction&nbsp;de l’objet en question. Vous trouverez les informations sur la solidité&nbsp;et les points de résistance des armes et des armures à la page 409.</p>\n<hr>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Si l’objet est une<strong> armure</strong>, les bonus qu’il confère à la CA sont diminués&nbsp;de moitié, arrondis à l’inférieur. On multiplie par deux le malus&nbsp;d’armure aux tests de compétence des armures cassées.</p>\n<hr>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Les objets affublés de l’état cassé, quel que soit leur type, peuvent&nbsp;être revendus pour la moitié de leur prix de revente normal (généralement&nbsp;5 % du prix d’achat de l’objet). Un objet peut être réparé avec le&nbsp;sort de réparation ou de réparation intégrale lancé par un personnage&nbsp;dont le niveau de lanceur de sorts est égal ou supérieur au niveau de&nbsp;l’objet.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Les objets perdent l’état cassé si le sort permet à l’objet de&nbsp;récupérer la moitié ou plus de son nombre de points de vie d’origine.</p>\n<hr>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Il est également possible de réparer les objets magiques avec la&nbsp;compétence de Mysticisme (voir page 144 pour plus d’informations)&nbsp;et les objets technologiques avec la compétence d’Ingénierie (voir&nbsp;page 142 pour plus d’informations). On peut réparer les objets hybrides&nbsp;avec l’une ou l’autre de ces compétences.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">La plupart des réparateurs&nbsp;d’objets magiques ou technologiques font payer 10 % du prix&nbsp;d’achat d’origine de l’objet pour réparer ces dégâts (ou plus si l’objet&nbsp;est détruit ou sévèrement endommagé).</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"CRB.273","type":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"target":{"value":"","type":""},"area":{"value":null,"units":null,"shape":"","effect":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":null,"additional":"","per":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"ability":"int","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"parts":[],"effect":""},"damage":{"parts":[]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"","dc":null,"descriptor":"negate"},"descriptors":[],"modifiers":[],"requirements":"Condition","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"abilityMods":{"parts":[]}},"sort":400000,"flags":{"dynamiceffects":{"equipActive":false,"alwaysActive":false}},"img":"systems/sfrpg/icons/conditions/Broken.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"YjE6UGzwOTfO9p4g","name":"Ébloui","permission":{"default":0},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&gt;@Compendium[sfrpg.rules.Conditions]</p>\n<hr>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Votre perception visuelle est amoindrie à cause d’une hyperstimulation&nbsp;de vos yeux. Vous subissez un malus de -1 aux jets d’attaque et&nbsp;aux tests de Perception basés sur la vue.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"CRB.275","type":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"target":{"value":"","type":""},"area":{"value":null,"units":null,"shape":"","effect":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":null,"additional":"","per":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"ability":"int","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"parts":[],"effect":""},"damage":{"parts":[]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"","dc":null,"descriptor":"negate"},"descriptors":[],"modifiers":[{"name":"Perception (Sight) Checks","modifier":-1,"type":"untyped","effectType":"skill","valueAffected":"per","enabled":true,"source":"Condition","notes":"For Perception (Sight) Checks.","modifierType":"constant","condition":"","subtab":"misc","_id":"94ec57e3-0c16-4efb-adee-96b699dafeea"},{"name":"Attack Rolls","modifier":-1,"type":"untyped","effectType":"all-attacks","valueAffected":"","enabled":true,"source":"Condition","notes":"Sight-Based Attack Rolls.","modifierType":"constant","condition":"","subtab":"misc","_id":"27306a31-a6cc-49ca-b587-f16ae175cdbd"}],"requirements":"Condition","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"abilityMods":{"parts":[]}},"sort":1200000,"flags":{"dynamiceffects":{"equipActive":false,"alwaysActive":false}},"img":"systems/sfrpg/icons/conditions/dazzled.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"ZacF0l6IwqBwToTJ","name":"Fiévreux","permission":{"default":0},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&gt;@Compendium[sfrpg.rules.Conditions]</p>\n<hr>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vous subissez un malus de -2 aux jets d’attaque, aux jets de dégâts&nbsp;des armes, aux jets de sauvegarde, aux tests de compétence et aux&nbsp;tests de caractéristique.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"CRB.277","type":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"target":{"value":"","type":""},"area":{"value":null,"units":null,"shape":"","effect":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":null,"additional":"","per":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"ability":"int","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"parts":[],"effect":""},"damage":{"parts":[]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"","dc":null,"descriptor":"negate"},"descriptors":[],"modifiers":[{"name":"Sickened","modifier":-2,"type":"untyped","effectType":"all-attacks","valueAffected":"acr","enabled":true,"source":"Condition","notes":"","modifierType":"constant","condition":"","subtab":"misc","_id":"2fc698d6-583b-4b2c-8a0a-8b010e5693b9"},{"name":"Sickened","modifier":-2,"type":"untyped","effectType":"all-damage","valueAffected":"","enabled":true,"source":"Condition","notes":"","modifierType":"constant","condition":"","subtab":"misc","_id":"286f24d9-87a4-4f71-b5a5-24ad173dfff5"},{"name":"Sickened","modifier":-2,"type":"untyped","effectType":"all-skills","valueAffected":"","enabled":true,"source":"Condition","notes":"","modifierType":"constant","condition":"","subtab":"misc","_id":"1352632d-7757-42f3-a617-07c71c7f1085"},{"name":"Sickened","modifier":-2,"type":"untyped","effectType":"saves","valueAffected":"","enabled":true,"source":"Condition","notes":"","modifierType":"constant","condition":"","subtab":"misc","_id":"216669b5-ea43-45df-8abf-51f8695ebbd3"}],"requirements":"Condition","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":fa