{"_id":"aAQ6SW6iK0EVq8Ce","name":"Chancelant","permission":{"default":0},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&gt;@Compendium[sfrpg.rules.Conditions]</p>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vous ne pouvez faire qu&rsquo;une action de mouvement ou qu&rsquo;une action&nbsp;simple par round, mais pas les deux, et vous ne pouvez pas effectuer&nbsp;d&rsquo;actions complexes. Vous pouvez toujours faire des actions rapides&nbsp;mais pas de r&eacute;actions.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"CRB.277","type":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"target":{"value":"","type":""},"area":{"value":null,"units":null,"shape":"","effect":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":null,"additional":"","per":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"ability":"int","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"parts":[],"effect":""},"damage":{"parts":[]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"","dc":null,"descriptor":"negate"},"descriptors":[],"modifiers":[],"requirements":"Condition","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"abilityMods":{"parts":[]}},"sort":3600000,"flags":{"dynamiceffects":{"equipActive":false,"alwaysActive":false}},"img":"systems/sfrpg/icons/conditions/staggered.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"lf8pbezocjYIvR9y","name":"Inconscient","permission":{"default":0},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&gt;@Compendium[sfrpg.rules.Conditions]</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&gt;@Compendium[sfrpg.conditions.Dying] + @Compendium[sfrpg.conditions.Stable] + @Compendium[sfrpg.conditions.Dead]</p>\n<hr>\n<p>Vous êtes mis KO et vous retrouvez @Compendium[world.conditions-fr.RxvbSB9ZgSCBu2jw]{Sans défense}. Vous tombez dans l’inconscience lorsque vos points de vie tombent à 0.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"CRB.277","type":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"target":{"value":"","type":""},"area":{"value":null,"units":null,"shape":"","effect":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":null,"additional":"","per":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"ability":"int","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"parts":[],"effect":""},"damage":{"parts":[]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"","dc":null,"descriptor":"negate"},"descriptors":[],"modifiers":[],"requirements":"Condition","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"abilityMods":{"parts":[]}},"sort":3800000,"flags":{"dynamiceffects":{"equipActive":false,"alwaysActive":false}},"img":"systems/sfrpg/icons/conditions/unconscious.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"nEJIWMKbPjqKuelo","name":"Mort","permission":{"default":0},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&gt;@Compendium[sfrpg.rules.Conditions]</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&gt;@Compendium[sfrpg.conditions.Dying] + @Compendium[sfrpg.conditions.Stable] + @Compendium[sfrpg.conditions.Unconscious]</p>\n<hr>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vous êtes mort lorsqu’il vous reste 0 point de vie, que vous n’êtes pas&nbsp;stabilisé et que vous n’avez plus aucun point de persévérance alors que&nbsp;vous devriez en perdre à cause de votre état agonisant ou quand vous&nbsp;subissez des dégâts pendant que vous êtes agonisant (voir Blessures et&nbsp;mort à partir de la page 250 pour plus d’informations). Vous pouvez également&nbsp;mourir à cause d’un affaiblissement temporaire de caractéristique,&nbsp;d’une diminution permanente de caractéristique ou de niveaux négatifs&nbsp;(voir page 252), ou en subissant des dégâts massifs (voir page 250).&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lorsque vous êtes mort, votre âme quitte votre corps et vous ne pouvez&nbsp;plus du tout agir. Vous ne pouvez plus recevoir de soins magiques&nbsp;ou ordinaires mais on peut vous ramener à la vie grâce à des moyens&nbsp;magiques ou technologiques capables d’accomplir cet exploit. Votre&nbsp;corps mort se décompose normalement à moins d’être conservé mais&nbsp;les moyens utilisés pour vous ramener à la vie restaurent également&nbsp;votre corps qui revient en pleine santé ou dans l’état qu’il était au moment&nbsp;où vous avez succombé (en fonction du sort ou de l’objet qui vous&nbsp;a ramené à la vie). Quelle que soit la méthode utilisée, la décomposition&nbsp;de votre corps, la rigidité cadavérique et les autres états qui affectent les&nbsp;cadavres ne sont plus un souci pour vous une fois ressuscité.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"CRB.275","type":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"target":{"value":"","type":""},"area":{"value":null,"units":null,"shape":"","effect":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":null,"additional":"","per":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"ability":"int","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"parts":[],"effect":""},"damage":{"parts":[]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"","dc":null,"descriptor":"negate"},"descriptors":[],"modifiers":[],"requirements":"Condition","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"abilityMods":{"parts":[]}},"sort":1300000,"flags":{"dynamiceffects":{"equipActive":false,"alwaysActive":false}},"img":"systems/sfrpg/icons/conditions/dead.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"nFBcsp5FS1Wi46Fc","name":"Enchevêtré","permission":{"default":0},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&gt;@Compendium[sfrpg.rules.Conditions]</p>\n<hr>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vous êtes empêtré.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Se retrouver enchevêtré réduit vos mouvements&nbsp;mais ne vous empêche pas complètement de vous déplacer,&nbsp;sauf si les entraves sont fixées à un objet immobile ou attachées par&nbsp;une force opposée. Vous vous déplacez à la moitié de votre vitesse de&nbsp;déplacement, vous ne pouvez plus courir ou charger et vous subissez&nbsp;un malus de -2 à la CA, aux jets d’attaque, aux jets de sauvegarde de&nbsp;Réflexes, aux tests d’initiative et aux tests de caractéristique et de&nbsp;compétence basés sur la Dextérité.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"CRB.275","type":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"target":{"value":"","type":""},"area":{"value":null,"units":null,"shape":"","effect":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":null,"additional":"","per":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"ability":"int","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"parts":[],"effect":""},"damage":{"parts":[]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"","dc":null,"descriptor":"negate"},"descriptors":[],"modifiers":[{"name":"Ensnared","modifier":-2,"type":"untyped","effectType":"ac","valueAffected":"both","enabled":true,"source":"Condition","notes":"","modifierType":"constant","condition":"","subtab":"misc","_id":"638286eb-b4c2-4411-9f7b-96cc2025f5b5"},{"name":"Ensnared","modifier":-2,"type":"untyped","effectType":"all-attacks","valueAffected":"","enabled":true,"source":"Condition","notes":"","modifierType":"constant","condition":"","subtab":"misc","_id":"b2b4ed27-5974-4270-aaca-fef4ec801837"},{"name":"Ensnared","modifier":-2,"type":"untyped","effectType":"save","valueAffected":"reflex","enabled":true,"source":"Condition","notes":"","modifierType":"constant","condition":"","subtab":"misc","_id":"82954220-2016-4bda-8a94-0bfeb4e3b23d"},{"name":"Ensnared","modifier":-2,"type":"untyped","effectType":"initiative","valueAffected":"","enabled":true,"source":"Condition","notes":"","modifierType":"constant","condition":"","subtab":"misc","_id":"92d7b355-64fd-428c-be24-ba01b6d64714"},{"name":"Ensnared","modifier":-2,"type":"untyped","effectType":"ability-skills","valueAffected":"dex","enabled":true,"source":"","notes":"","modifierType":"constant","condition":"","subtab":"misc","_id":"90f589f4-df63-4311-8c3c-2f779b32a0c1"}],"requirements":"Condition","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"abilityMods":{"parts":[]}},"sort":1700000,"flags":{"dynamiceffects":{"equipActive":false,"alwaysActive":false}},"img":"systems/sfrpg/icons/conditions/entangled.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"nywSVEeDvp1bk7L3","name":"Secoué","permission":{"default":0},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&gt;@Compendium[sfrpg.rules.Conditions]</p>\n<hr>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vous subissez un malus de -2 aux jets d’attaque, aux jets de sauvegarde,&nbsp;aux tests de compétence et aux tests de caractéristique lorsque&nbsp;vous êtes secoué.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Si vous êtes déjà secoué puis assujetti à un autre&nbsp;effet qui devrait lui aussi vous secouer, la durée du deuxième effet&nbsp;s’ajoute à celle de l’état secoué.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"CRB.277","type":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"target":{"value":"","type":""},"area":{"value":null,"units":null,"shape":"","effect":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":null,"additional":"","per":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"ability":"int","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"parts":[],"effect":""},"damage":{"parts":[]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"","dc":null,"descriptor":"negate"},"descriptors":[],"modifiers":[{"name":"Shaken","modifier":-2,"type":"untyped","effectType":"all-attacks","valueAffected":"acr","enabled":true,"source":"Condition","notes":"","modifierType":"constant","condition":"","subtab":"misc","_id":"05a1ec53-c4b6-4699-b4a9-8dc0ef0aac8f"},{"name":"Shaken","modifier":-2,"type":"untyped","effectType":"saves","valueAffected":"","enabled":true,"source":"Condition","notes":"","modifierType":"constant","condition":"","subtab":"misc","_id":"36603808-e34d-4337-972c-8272fa926420"},{"name":"Shaken","modifier":-2,"type":"untyped","effectType":"all-skills","valueAffected":"","enabled":true,"source":"Condition","notes":"","modifierType":"constant","condition":"","subtab":"misc","_id":"15405124-f002-4c28-a0a6-1a1fe740eec9"}],"requirements":"Condition","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"abilityMods":{"parts":[]}},"sort":3300000,"flags